-ªU<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:3119;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2012-07-18 13:55:11";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-18 20:55:11";s:12:"post_content";s:2796:"<div align="center"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><u>City of Los Angeles</u></strong></span></div>
<div align="center"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><u>Department of Personnel Consolidation</u></strong></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">E<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">ffective <span id="OBJ_PREFIX_DWT281_com_zimbra_date">July 1</span>, 2012 Phase One of the new Human Resources Shared Services model was implemented. As a result, the Personnel Department is now responsible for providing the full array of Human Resources services to fifthteen city departments/bureaus. In return, most of the affected departments functionally transferred a total of 70 members of their Human Resources staff.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Phase two of this model, scheduled to begin on <span id="OBJ_PREFIX_DWT282_com_zimbra_date">January 1, 2013</span> will bring an additional eight departments and thirty-five employees.</span></div>
	<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
	<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The new departments have been assigned to one of three groups. The three groups and their corresponding departments are listed below. Most of the employees who are functionally transferred will remain in their current locations.</span></div>
	<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
	<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Human Resources Centralization represents a new and exciting change for the Personnel Department.</span></div>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><u><strong>Group 1: Jim Abalos, Personnel Director III</strong></u><br />
		Public Works &ndash; OMES<br />
		Contract Admin.<br />
		Engineering<br />
		Sanitation<br />
		Street Lighting<br />
		Street Services<br />
		Animal Services</span></p>
	<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><u><strong>Group 2: Bill Weeks, Personnel Director III</strong></u><br />
		Transportation<br />
		Personnel<br />
		ITA<br />
		Planning<br />
		Cultural Affairs<br />
		CDD<br />
		Disability<br />
		Aging<br />
		Finance</span></p>
	<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><u><strong>Group 3: Dan Yoshimura, Personnel Director III</strong></u><br />
		General Services<br />
		El Pueblo<br />
		Emergency Mgt<br />
		Neighborhood Emp<br />
		Convention Ctr<br />
		Housing<br />
		Building &amp; Safety</span></p>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
